      <textAnnotation id="sid-813B9249-8623-4877-9AA2-BA5191AEFF60" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Cascading feed to prioritize the order</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-05382191-19B3-4D17-838C-72C97EB8C70B" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>1. Factory &amp; Related Apps: Scheduler, Kitting, MES, CIBR, ISET, MPL, Prospal, Spectrum, Waybill, Ship Memo 

2. Refer Manufacturing E2E-74 flow and Architecture Diagram to understand detailed level interfacing

</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-B022CE2C-B9FD-48DB-9C5D-3EFAC12F73D8" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
